### Description
When Teku is in sync but Geth is still syncing, we don't seem to track blocks from gossip correctly and fall behind around 40-50 blocks before long sync kicks back in and catches us up again.  This is suboptimal for both Teku and Geth as Geth will sync better if it can track the latest chain head all the time.

